metadata.name: Ancientz X Blip - Setsunai #1/83
metadata.description:
Genesis drop from 20-year-old producer Ancientz out of Oklahoma, USA.

From the artist: Music is a universal language that I'm learning to speak. No matter the genre, there is always a complex process that creates a beautiful result in the end. My only dream is to share with the world what I create. If I'm not making music, I'll either be working or playing a game to help the music making process not be repetitive or daunting.
